<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">A linha de Boiadeiros &eacute; a primeira na escala vibrat&oacute;ria de evolu&ccedil;&atilde;o dos Guias de Direita, onde se apresentam os esp&iacute;ritos egressos das Linhas dos Guardi&otilde;es. Ou seja, o Boiadeiro pode ser visto como um Exu que adquiriu m&eacute;rito e decidiu se integrar &agrave;s Linhas da Direita. S&atilde;o conhecidos tamb&eacute;m como Caboclos Boiadeiros. Atuam nas sete Linhas da Umbanda, ora regidos pelo Orix&aacute; Ogum, ora pelo Orix&aacute; Oi&aacute; (Ians&atilde;). Trazem, como simbologia, o la&ccedil;o e o chicote. S&atilde;o audazes e aguerridos. Atuam como refreadores de &ldquo;demandas&rdquo; e do baixo astral, rigorosos no trato com a espiritualidade &ldquo;trevosa&rdquo;. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Os Boiadeiros na Umbanda s&atilde;o entidades espirituais de homens que trabalharam no campo, na rudeza da condu&ccedil;&atilde;o do gado e na dureza da lida do sert&atilde;o. Operam nos terreiros com seu la&ccedil;o e seu grito caracter&iacute;stico, capturando esp&iacute;ritos deca&iacute;dos e quiumbas que atormentam os consulentes, encaminhando-os para as falanges de socorro e recupera&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><u><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Algumas caracter&iacute;sticas dos boiadeiros</span></span></span></u></strong></span></span></p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Sauda&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">: Jetru&aacute;! X&ecirc;tro! Marrumba X&ecirc;tro! Getru&aacute; boiadeiro! (Salve aquele que tem bra&ccedil;o forte, pulso firme).</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Dia da Semana: </span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Quinta-feira.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Bebidas:</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"> Cacha&ccedil;a com mel, batida de coco, caf&eacute;, caf&eacute; com cacha&ccedil;a.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Fumo: </span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Cigarro de palha e fumo de rolo.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Cozinha:</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"> Feij&atilde;o tropeiro, ab&oacute;bora com farofa.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Utens&iacute;lios: </span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Chap&eacute;u de couro, la&ccedil;os, berrantes, guias de couro tran&ccedil;ado.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Irradia&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></span></span></strong><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;"> A irradia&ccedil;&atilde;o depende do Orix&aacute;.</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

